
read every filename into array.
iterate through array

\..*$ - replace everything after period with nothing
(?i)(?=\s-\sScene).*$ - replace " - Scene" and everything after with nothing (case insensitive)
(?i)(?=\s-\sCD).*$ - replace " - Scene" and everything after with nothing (case insensitive)

remove duplicates

show ui-grid in modal with all elements in array so that they can be edited and added to db.
